text: The Curious Dr. Humpp also known as La venganza del sexo (Spanish for "revenge of sex") is a 1969 Argentine science fiction horror movie directed by Emilio Vieyra and starring Ricardo Bauleo, Gloria Prat, Aldo Barbero. ==Other websites== * * * Category:1969 movies Category:1960s science fiction movies Category:1969 horror movies Category:Argentine science fiction movies Category:Argentine horror movies Category:Movies directed by Emilio Vieyra
title: The Curious Dr. Humpp
